{"tid":1298452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"713 光復上水online再次上線——行動討論","createTime":"2019-07-09T01:29:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T14:45:14.000Z","uid":8230,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"310a2cccb880bf848b4e09e1f28c699eef0596e5","tid":1298452,"uid":8230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pG2a75C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpG2a75C.png&h=2261a0c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同大媽一齊濕平真係諗起都興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<code>我冇野講 我唔解鎖 我搵律師 唔好凶我 我投訴你</code>"},{"pid":"39e955c4179e1b2b762d9dd91ece1da36a188d97","tid":1298452,"uid":8230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:30:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b26dda9494dcd3561e7087d61db4e709ca37f076","tid":1298452,"uid":8230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n還我上水！！！"},{"pid":"af7d58348cc58f63aa13476ecd35c7a18d2c48b2","tid":1298452,"uid":8230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:48:52.000Z","msg":"北區人出嚟啊！！！！"},{"pid":"b4003a12eb36a3c4eba54fb0c2aa6b79ee33e955","tid":1298452,"uid":40287,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:58:08.000Z","msg":"上水啲街其實好細，如果人數太多，場面應該幾轟動，一班忍咗好耐嘅上水居民應該都會出嚟，雖然上水水貨客嘅問題唔係話一次遊行可以解決到。<br />\n<br />\n其實呢啲光復上水嘅運動，金金佢哋搞過好多次，但人數愈嚟愈少，記得有一次去到石湖畀啲商戶衝出嚟話阻住晒，指住我哋話「得幾十友咋你哋，上水有十萬人，又唔見其他人出嚟反對？」<br />\n<br />\n嗰吓有啲灰，因為出席人數愈嚟愈少，好多人都覺得呢啲遊行冇乜作用，雖然咁多場光復運動出現後，政府整咗啲 措施減少中國人對上水嘅衝擊，但作用唔大，將石湖塞爆嘅中國人有增冇減，上水又係建制地方，林卓廷做唔到啲乜。<br />\n<br />\n有人話上水冇得救，但如果可以喚醒更多人嘅關注，可能會令件事有一絲轉機都未定。"},{"pid":"70fa92f859ec227ccdc4c7f073df493d9b13964d","tid":1298452,"uid":134054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:02:42.000Z","msg":"一定要去"},{"pid":"2f7d78636a17af6f956e335b5262b7325ffb5a2d","tid":1298452,"uid":68632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:10:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79835608c5387fc9db5134b1f67d437df579dbac","tid":1298452,"uid":147643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9bf758e5585a7b9d86a099d402ff3a37d3e1ec5","tid":1298452,"uid":124212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:17:11.000Z","msg":"<code>我無嘢講 我要見律師 我唔解鎖電話 我唔簽任何文件 我要去醫院驗傷</code>"},{"pid":"ba23abc97db7f730048ffbba8b76832f5f3fc486","tid":1298452,"uid":8230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:31:03.000Z","msg":"<code>我冇野講 我唔解鎖 我搵律師 唔好凶我 我投訴你</code>"},{"pid":"6d4b70819b71c9a3e97beb9e2dd0d5cae2678a42","tid":1298452,"uid":23047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:49:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e271ce012da8319a5e4e13e6297b48f159e84b5c","tid":1298452,"uid":59016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:49:27.000Z","msg":"有冇不反對通知書"},{"pid":"47dfd67084a8bfb1e18d07f347409dc6b79acc39","tid":1298452,"uid":180808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e271ce012da8319a5e4e13e6297b48f159e84b5c","tid":1298452,"uid":59016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:49:27.000Z","msg":"有冇不反對通知書"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:24:49.000Z","msg":"我都想知"},{"pid":"7bc0fd2de3ea1efaac58a92de693f0293639152d","tid":1298452,"uid":180808,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:25:19.000Z","msg":"人地屯門都成功左啦<br />\n<br />\n上水都要爭取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/